{{Infobox dungeon |name = Seaside Cave |image = [[File:Seaside Cave.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Seaside Cave. |tokens = 246,500 |location = Unova Route 21 }} '''Seaside Cave''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Unova]]. It initially has 81 tiles arranged in an 9x9 square, including 9 chest tiles, 21 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 4,203,000 HP.
